      "side": 1,
      "message": "In addition to using fingerprint to identify the metadata, shall we also allow user to provide the exact key value pairs? It probably doesn\u0027t make sense for large blob value. However, I assume the `git_revision` tag today will be converted to metadata and I think it will be much easier just to provide `git_revision:XXX` directly instead of having a extra step to find the fingerprint of the metadata.WDYT?",
